Package Hospital.Patient

Class Summary
Diagnosis Holds the diagnosis for a patient
DiagnosisApproveCommand Approves a diagnosis and schedules its associated treatment, and undoes that later if necessary
DiagnosisCommand Creates a diagnosis (with or without second opinion), and undoes that later if necessary
DiagnosisFactory Creates simple diagnoses (without second opinion)
DiagnosisInfo A reference to a diagnosis.
DiagnosisSecondOpinion A diagnosis which requires a second opinion
DiagnosisSecondOpinionFactory Creates diagnoses which require a second opinion
Patient A patient, who can be diagnosed, tested and treated
PatientFactory Creates patients
